column1: # this data was copied and pasted from the original excel file. I deleted all of the plant trait data to focus on the arthropods.  I then transferred all of the arthropod data from the notes section into new columns of data.  Had to move some of the notes to the appropriate row because they were typed in out of sequence with "other arthropods".  Note that just because there is a zero for "other arthropods" doesn't mean there couldn't have been arthropod data entered in the notes (inaccuracy in transcribing data in the field). For the new data added from the notes column, I replaced all blank values with zeros, because that is what they actually reflect.
